# Business Requirements Document (BRD)

## Business Objective
To improve financial visibility and operational efficiency through structured financial analysis and KPI reporting.

## Key Requirements
- Track departmental budgets and expenses
- Identify cost overruns and savings opportunities
- Monitor operational KPIs
- Generate management-ready reports

## Stakeholders
- Finance Team
- Operations Management
- Senior Leadership

## Success Criteria
- Accurate financial reporting
- Clear visibility into cost trends
- Actionable insights for decision-making
